title: Thom Hartmann Program - October 25 2013
description:
October 25, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 

Hour One: Brunch With Bernie - Senator Bernie Sanders (I-VT) takes your calls

Hour Two: Grenada...30 years since the U.S. invasion - Don Rojas, former Press Secretary-Prime Minister of Grenada, Maurice Bishop

Hour Three: Is the Tea Party like the KKK...or not?  Congressman Alan Grayson (D-FL, 9th District)
